hadiths[127]{hadithnumber,text}:
682,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab maahe-Ramzan ki pehli raat aati hai, to shetan aur sarkash jin jakad diye jatey hain, jahannam ke darwazey band kar diye jatey hain, un mein sey koi bhi darwaza khola nahin jata. aur jannat ke darwazey khol diye jatey hain, un mein sey koi bhi darwaza band nahin kiya jata, pukarney wala pukarta hai : khair ke talab-gaar ! aagey badh , aur shar ke talabgar ! ruk ja padhi. aur aag sey Allah ke bahut sey azad kiye huye bandey hain (to ho sakta hai ke to bhi unhi mein sey ho) aur aisa (Ramzan ki) har raat ko hota hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Abdur-Rehman bin Auf , ibne-Masood aur Salman (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
683,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney eman key sath aur sawab ki niyat sey Ramzan key rozey rakhey aur uski raaton mein qiyam kiya to uskey sabiqa (pichhle) gunah padhi. bakhsh diye jaeyngey. aur jisney eman ke sath aur sawab ki niyat sey shabe-qadr mein qiyam kiya to uskey bhi sabiqa gunah bakhsh diye jaeyngey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki (pichhli) hadees , jisey abu-Bakar bin Ayash ney riwayat ki hai gharib hai, usey hum abu-Bakar bin Ayash ki riwayat ki tarah jisey unhoney ba-tareeq : (Aamash an abi Saleh an abi Hurera) riwayat ki hai. abu-Bakar hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is hadees key mutalliq puchha to unhoney basanad (Hasan bin Rabee an Ubai an al-Aamash) Mujahid ka qol naqal kiya ke jab maahe-ramzan ki pehli raat hoti hai … phir aagey unhoney puri hadees bayan ki. 3- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : ye hadees merey nazdik abu-Bakar bin Ayash ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai."
684,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''us maah (ramzan) sey eik ya do din pehley (ramzan ke istaqbal ki niyat sey) rozey na rakho, siwaye iskey ke usdin aisa roza aa padey jisey tum pehley sey rakhtey aa rahey ho padhi. aur (ramzan ka ( chaand dekh kar roza rakho aur (shawwaal ka ( chaand dekh kar hi roza rakhna band karo. agar aasman par baadal ho jaaey to mahiney ke tees din shumar kar lo, phir roza rakhna band karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein baaz Sahaba kiram sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm ke nazdik isi par amal hai. wo is baat ko makrooh samajhtey hain ke aadmi maahe-ramzan ke aaney sey pehley Ramzan ke istaqbal mein rozey rakhey , aur agar kisi aadmi ka (kisi khas din mein) roza rakhney ka mamool ho aur wo din Ramzan sey pehley aa padey to un ke nazdik us din roza rakhney mein koi harj nahin."
685,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ramzan sey eik ya do din pehley (ramzan ke istaqbal mein) roza na rakho siwaye iskey ke aadmi us din roza rakhta aa raha ho to usey rakhey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
686,"Hum Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) key paas they ke eik bhuni hui bakri laee gaee to unhoney kaha : khaao ye sun kar eik sahab alag goshey (kone) mein ho gaey aur kaha : main rozey sey hun, is par Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : jisney kisi aisey din roza rakha jis mein logon ko shubha ho padhi. (ke Ramzan ka chaand huwa hai ya nahin) usney Abul-Qaasim Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki nafarmani ki. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera aur Anas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hai, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram aur unkey baad Tabe-een mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, yehi Sufiyan Sory , Malik bin Anas , Abdullah bin Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai. in logon ney us din roza rakhney ko makrooh qarar diya hai jis mein shubha ho, (ke Ramzan ka chaand huwa hai ya nahin) aur un mein sey aksar ka khayal hai ke agar wo us din roza rakhey aur wo maahe-ramzan ka din ho to wo uskey badley eik din ki qaza karey."
687,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ramzan ke liye Shoban ke chaand ki ginti karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees gharib hai. 2- hum isey is tarah abu-Muaawia hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain aur sahih wo riwayat hai jo (Abda bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) ne) ba-tareeq (Muhammad bin Amr an abi Salma an abi Huraira an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat ki hai ke aap ney farmaya : ''ramzan ke istaqbal main eik ya do din pehley roza shuru na kar do, isi tarah ba-tareeq : (Yahya bin abi Kasir an abi Salama an abi Huraira an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
688,"Ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ramzan sey pehley padhi. roza na rakho, chaand dekh kar roza rakho, aur dekh kar hi band karo, aur agar badal aadey aa jaey to mahiney ke tees din purey karo.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai aur kaee sanadon sey ye hadees riwayat ki gaee hai. padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , abu-Bakra aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
689,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ke sath tees din ke rozey rakhney sey ziyada 29 din ke rozey rakhey hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein umr , Abu-Hurera , Aaisha , Saad bin Abi Waqas , ibne-Abbas , ibne-Umar , Anas , Jabir , Umme-Salma aur Abu-Bakra (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mahina 29 din ka (bhi) hota hai.''"
690,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apni biwiyon sey eik maah key liye elaa kiya (yani apni biwiyon sey na milney ki qism khai) phir aap ney apney baala-khaney mein 29 din qiyam kiya (phir aap apni biwiyon ke paas aaye) to logon ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! aap ney to eik mahiney ka elaa kiya tha? aap ney farmaya : ''mahina 29 din ka (bhi) hota hai.''Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
691,"eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) ne Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar kaha : mainey chaand dekha hai, aap ney farmaya : ''kya tum gawahi detey ho ke Allah ke siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin aur kya gawahi detey ho ke Muhammad Allah key Rasool hain?'' usney kaha : haan deta hun, aap ney farmaya : ''Bilaal ! logon mein aelan kar do ke wo kal roza rakhen.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas ki hadees mein ikhtilaf hai. Sufiyan Sory waghera ney ba-tareeq : (Simaak an Akrama an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) mursalan riwayat ki hai. aur Simaak ke aksar shagirdon ney bhi ba-tareeq : (Simaak an Akramaa an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) mursalan hi riwayat ki hai. 2- aksar ehle-ilm ka amal isi hadees par hai. wo kehtey hain ke maahe-ramzan ke rozon ke silsiley main eik aadmi ki gawahi qubul ki jaeygi. aur ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur ehle-Koofa bhi isi ke qaail hain. 3- Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke roza baghair do aadmiyon ki gawahi ke na rakha jaeyga. lekin roza band karney ke silsiley mein ehle-ilm mein koi ikhtilaf nahin ke is mein do aadmi ki gawahi qubul hogi."
692,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Eid ke dono mahiney Ramzan padhi. aur zul-hijja kam nahin hotey (yani dono 29 din ke nahin hotey).'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Bakra ki hadees Hasan hai. 2- ye hadees Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Bakra sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan riwayat ki hai. 3- Ahmed bin Hanbal kehtey hain : is hadees ''eid ke dono mahiney kam nahin hotey'' ka matlab ye hai ke Ramzan aur zul-hijja dono eik hi saal ke andar kam nahin hotey padhi. agar in dono mein koi kam hoga yani eik 29 din ka hoga to doosra pura yani tees din ka hoga. 4- Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke iska matlab ye hai ke agar ye 29 din ke hon to bhi sawab ke aetbar sey kam na hongey, Is-haq bin Raahviya key mazhab ki taraf sey dono mahiney eik saal mein kam ho saktey hain yani dono 29 din ke ho saktey hain."
693,"Umme Fazal binte Haris ney unhen Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas Sham bheja, to main Sham aaya aur mainey unki zarurat puri ki, aur (usi darmiyan) Ramzan ka chaand nikal aaya, aur main Sham hi mein tha ke humney Jume ki raat ko chaand dekha, phir main mahiney key aakhir mein Madina aaya to ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney mujh sey wahan ke halaat puchhey phir unhoney chaand ka zikr kiya aur kaha : tum logon ney chaand kab dekha tha? mainey kaha : hum ne usey Jume ki raat ko dekha tha, to unhoney kaha : kya tum ney bhi Juma ki raat ko dekha tha? to mainey kaha : logon ney isey dekha aur unhoney rozey rakhey aur Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney bhi roza rakha , is par ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : lekin hamney isey hafta (saneechar) ki raat ko dekha, to hum barabar rozey sey rahengey yahan tak ke hum tees din purey kar lein, ya hum 29 ka chaand dekh lein, to mainey kaha : kya aap Muawiya ke chaand dekhney aur roza rakhney ko kaafi nahi samjhoge? unhoney kaha : nahin, hamein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aisa hi hukm diya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke har shehar walon ke liye un ke khud chaand dekhney ka aetbar hoga."
694,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisey khajoor muyassar ho, to chahiye ke wo usi sey roza kholey , aur jisey khajoor muyassar na ho to chahiye ke wo pani sey kholey kyonkey pani pakizah chiz hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Salman bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 2- hum nahin jantey ke Anas ki hadees Saeed bin Aamir ke ilawa kisi aur ney bhi Shoba sey riwayat ki hai, ye hadees ghair mehfooz hai padhi. , hum iski koi asal abdul-Azeez ki riwayat sey jisey unhoney Anas sey riwayat ki ho nahin jantey , aur Shoba ke shagirdon ney ye hadees ba-tareeq : (Shoba an Aasim Al Ahwal an Hafsa binte Sireen an Rubaab an Salman bin Aamir an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat ki hai, aur ye Saeed bin Aamir ki riwayat sey ziyada sahih hai, kuchh aur logon ney iski ba-tareeq : « Shoba an Aasim an Hafsaa binte Sireen an Salman) riwayat ki hai aur is mein Shoba ki Rubab sey riwayat karney ka zikr nahin kiya gaya hai aur sahih wo hai jisey Sufiyan Sory , ibn Uena aur deegar kaee logon ney ba-tareeq : (Aasim A Ahwal an Hafsaa binte Sireen an Rubaab an Salman bin Aamir) riwayat ki hai, aur ibne Aun kehtey hain : (An Umme Raayah binte Sule' an Salman bin Aamir) aur Rubaab hi darasal Umme Raayah hain."
695,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum mein sey koi iftaar karey to chaahiye ke khajoor sey iftaar karey kyonkey is mein barkat hai aur jisey (khajoor) muyassar na ho to wo pani sey iftaar karey kyonkey ye pakizah chiz hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
696,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam (maghrib) padhney sey pehley chand tar khajuron sey iftaar kartey they, aur agar tar khajuren na hotin to chand khushk khajuron sey aur agar khushk khajuren bhi muyassar na hotin to pani ke chand ghoont pi letey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- aur ye bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sardiyon mein chand khajuron sey iftaar kartey aur garmiyon mein pani sey."
697,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Roze ka din wohi hai jis din tum sab roza rakhtey ho aur iftaar ka din wohi hai jab sab Eidul-Fitr manatey ho aur Azhaa ka din wohi hai jab sab Eid manatey ho.''Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- baaz ehle-ilm ney is hadees ki tashreeh yun ki hai ke roze aur Eidul-Fitr ijtimaaiyat aur sabhi loogon ke sath hone chahiye.
698,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab raat aa jaey, aur din chala jaey aur suraj doob jaey to tum ney iftaar kar liya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abi Aufi aur abu Saeed Khudri sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
699,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''log barabar khair mein rahengey padhi. jab tak ke wo iftaar mein jaldi karengey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , ibne-Abbas , Aaisha aur Anas bin Malik (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- aur yehi qol hai jisey Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ney ikhtiyar kiya hai, un logon ney iftaar mein jaldi karney ko mustahab jana hai aur isi ke Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi qaail hain."
700,Ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah farmata hai : mujhey merey bandon mein sab sey ziyada mehbub wo hain jo iftaar mein jaldi karney waley hain.''
701,Auzaai sey isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
702,"Main aur Masruq dono Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ke paas gaey, hamney arz kiya : Ummul-momenin ! Sahaba mein sey do aadmi hain, un mein sey eik iftaar jaldi karta hai aur namaz padhi. bhi jaldi padhta hai aur doosra iftaar mein takheer karta hai aur namaz bhi der sey padhta hai padhi. unhoney kaha : wo kon hai jo iftaar jaldi karta hai aur namaz bhi jaldi padhta hai, hamney kaha : wo Abdullah bin Masood hain, is par unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam isi tarah kartey they aur doosrey Abu-Musa hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Abu Atiyaa ka naam Maalik bin abi Aamir Hamdaani hai aur unhen ibne Aamir Hamdaani bhi kaha jata hai. aur ibne Aamir hi ziyada sahih hai."
703,"Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : hamney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ke sath sehri ki, phir hum namaz ke liye khadey huye, Anas kehtey hain ke mainey puchha : uski miqdaar kitni thi? padhi. unhoney kaha : pachas aayaton ke (padhney ke) ba-qadr."
704,"Hisham sey isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai albatta is mein yun hai : pachas aayaton ke padhney ke ba-qadr. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai, in logon ney sehri mein der karney ko pasand kiya hai."
705,"Mujhse merey baap Talq bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan kiya ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''khaao piyo , tumhen khaney peeney sey chamakti aur chadhti hui subah yani subah na rokey padhi. khaatey peetey raho, yahan tak ke surkhi phail jaaey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Talq bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Adi bin Hatim , Abu-Zar aur Samura (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- isi par ehle-ilm ka amal hai ke rozedaar par khana peena haram nahin hota jab tak ke Fajr ki surkh chaudi roshni namoodaar (zaahir) na ho jaaey , aur yehi aksar ehle-ilm ka qol hai."
706,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tumhen sehri khaney sey Bilal ki Azan baaz (roke) na rakhey aur na hi lambi Fajr baaz (roke) rakhey , haan wo Fajr baaz rakhey jo kinaron mein phailti hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
707,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo (rozedaar) jhoot bolnaa aur is par amal karna na chhodey to Allah Taala ko uska khana-peena chhodney ki koi zarurat nahin hai'.'  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
708,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sehri khaao, kyonkey sehri mein barkat hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Abdullah bin Masood , Jabir bin Abdullah , ibne-Abbas , Amr bin al-Aas , Arbaz bin Saariya , Utba bin Abdullah aur Abu-Darda (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke aap ney farmaya : ''hamarey rozon aur ehle-kitab ke rozon mein farq sehri khaney ka hai.''"
709,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey yehi hadees riwayat kartey hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- aur ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ehale Misr Musa bin Ali kehtey hain aur ehale Iraaq Musa bin Ulaee kehtey hain aur wo Musa bin Ulaee bin Ribah hain.
710,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Fateh Makka ke saal Makka ki taraf nikley to aap ney roza rakha , aur aap key sath logon ney bhi roza rakha , yahan tak ke aap Kraae Ghameem par pahunchey to aap sey arz kiya gaya ke logon par roza rakhna giraan ho raha hai aur log aap key amal ko dekh rahey hain. (yani muntazir hain ke aap kuchh karen) to aap ney Asr key baad eik piyala pani mangaa kar piya, log aap ko dekh rahey they, to un mein sey baaz ney roza tod diya aur baaz rakhey rahey. aap ko malum huwa ke kuch log (ab bhi) rozey sey hain, aap ney farmaya : ''yehi log nafarman hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Kaab bin Aasim, ibne-Abbas aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke aap ney farmaya : ''safar mein roza rakhna neki nahin hai.'' 4- safar mein roza rakhney key silsiley mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai, Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka khayal hai ke safar mein roza na rakhna afzal hai, yahan tak baaz logon ki raey hai ke jab wo safar mein roza rakh ley to wo safar sey lotney key baad phir dobara rakhey, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ney bhi safar mein roza na rakhney ko tarjeeh di hai. 5- aur Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka kehna hai ke agar wo taqat paey aur roza rakhey to yehi behtar aur afzal hai. Sufiyan Sory , Malik bin Anas aur Abdullah bin Mubarak isi key qaail hain. 6- Shafai kehtey hain : Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ke qol ''safar mein roza rakhna neki nahin'' aur jis waqt aap ko malum huwa ke kuchh log rozey sey hain to aap ka ye farmana ke ''yehi log nafarman hain'' aisey shakhs key liye hai jis ka dil Allah ki di hui rukhsat (chhot) aur ijazat ko qubul na karey, lekin jo log safar mein roza na rakhney ko jayaz samajhtey huye roza rakhey aur uski quwat bhi rakhta ho to ye mujhey ziyada pasand hai."
711,"Hamza bin Amr Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey safar mein roza rakhney key barey mein puchha , wo khud musalsal roza rakha kartey they to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''chaho to rakho aur chaho to na rakho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha ki hadees ke Hamza bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey poochha, Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Anas bin Malik , abu Saeed Khudri , Abdullah bin Masood , Abdullah bin Amr , Abu-Darda aur Hamza bin Amr Aslami (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
712,Hum log Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ke sath Ramzan mein safar kartey to na aap roza rakhney waley ke roza rakhney par nakeer kartey aur na hi roza na rakhney waley ke roza na rakhney par. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
713,"Hum log Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ke sath safar kartey they to hum mein sey baaz rozey sey hotey aur baaz rozey sey na hotey. to na to roza na rakhney wala rakhney waley par ghussa karta aur na hi roza rakhney waley na rakhney waley par , unka khayal tha ke jisi quwat ho wo roza rakhey to behtar hai, aur jisney kamzori mehsus ki aur roza na rakha to bhi behtar hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
714,"Unhoney ibne Musaiyab sey safar mein roza rakhney ke barey mein puchha to ibne Musaiyab ney bayan kiya ke umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : hamney Ramzan mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ke sath do ghazwey kiye. ghazwae-badar aur Fateh Makka , hamney in dono mein rozey nahin rakhey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- Abu Saeed Khudri sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai unhoney Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai ke aap ney (logon ko) eik ghazwey mein iftaar ka hukm diya. umr bin Khattab sey bhi isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai. albatta unhoney roza rakhney ki rukhsat (chhoot) dushman sey mudbhed ki surat mein di hai. aur baaz ehle-ilm isi ke qaail hain."
715,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ke sawaron ney hum par raat mein hamla kiya, to main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ke paas aaya , mainey aap ko paya ke aap dophar ka khana kha rahey they, aap ney farmaya : '' aao kha lo''  mainey arz kiya : ''main rozey sey hun.'' aap ney farmaya : ''qarib aao, main tumhen rozey key barey mein bataaun , Allah Taala ney musafir sey roza aur aadhi namaz padhi. maaf kar di hai, hamila aur doodh pilaney wali aurat sey bhi roze ko maaf kar diya hai. Allah ki qism Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamila aur doodh pilaney wali aurat dono lafz kahe ya un mein sey koi eik lafz kaha, to haaye afsos apney aap par ke mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath kyon nahin khaya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas bin Malik Ka'bi ki hadees Hasan hai, Anas bin Malik ki uskey ilawa koi aur hadees hum nahin jantey jisey unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki ho. 2- is bab mein Abu Umayya sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. 4- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke hamila aur doodh pilaney wali aurten roza nahin rakhengi, baad mein qaza kerengi, aur fuqaraa aur miskinon ko khana khilaeyngi. Sufiyan , Maalik , Shafai aur Ahmed isi ke qaail hain. 5- baaz kehtey hain : wo roza nahin rakhengi balke fuqaraa aur miskinon ko khana khilaeyngi. aur un par koi qaza nahin aur agar wo qaza karna chahen to unpar khana khilana wajib nahin. Is-haq bin Raahviya isi ke qaail hain."
716,"Eik aurat ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar kaha : meri behan mar gaee hai. is par musalsal do maah ke rozey they. bataiye main kya karun? aap ney farmaya : ''zara bataao agar tumhari behan par qarz hota to kya tum usey ada kartiin?'' usney kaha : haan (ada karti), aap ney farmaya : ''to Allah ka haq us sey bhi bada hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Barida , ibne-Umar aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
717,"Aamash sey isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna ke Abu-Khalid Ahmar ney Aamash sey ye hadees bahut umda tareeqey sey riwayat ki hai. 4- Abu-Khalid Ahmar ke ilawa deegar logon ney bhi isey Aamash sey Abu-Khalid ki riwayat ke jasi riwayat kiya hai, Abu-Muaawia ney aur doosrey kaee aur logon ney ye hadees ba-tareeq : (Aamash an Muslim Al Bateen an Saeed bin Juber an ibne-Abbas an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat ki hai, is mein in logon ney Salma bin Kuheil ka zikr nahin kiya hai. aur na hi Ata aur Mujahid ke wastey ka, Abu-Khalid ka naam Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Hayyan hai."
718,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo is haalat mein marey ke is par eik maah ke roze baqi ho to uski taraf sey har din key badley eik miskeen ko khana khilaya jaey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees ko hum sirf isi sanad sey marfoo jantey hain. 2- sahih baat ye hai ke ye ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey maqoof hai yani unhin ka qol hai. 3- is barey mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai. baaz kehtey hain ke maiyat ki taraf sey rozey rakhey jaeyngey. ye qol Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka hai. ye dono kehtey hain : jab maiyat par nazar waley rozey hon to uski taraf sey roza rakha jaeyga, aur jab is par Ramzan ki qaza wajib ho to uski taraf sey miskinon aur faqiron ko khana khilaya jaeyga, Malik , Sufiyan aur Shafai kehtey hain ke koi kisi ki taraf sey roza nahin rakheyga."
719,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''teen chizon sey roze-daar ka roza nahin toot-ta : pachhna lagwaaney sey padhi. , qai aa janey sey aur ehtilaam ho janey sey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees mehfooz nahin hai. 2- Abdullah bin Zaid bin Aslam aur Abdul-Azeez bin Muhammad aur deegar kaee riwayaton ney ye hadees Zaid bin Aslam sey mursalan riwayat ki hai. aur is mein in logon ney Abu Saeed Khudri ke wastey ka zikr nahin kiya hai. 3- Abdur-Rehman bin Zaid bin Aslam hadees mein zaeef maaney jatey hain. 4- mainey Abu-Daawood Sijzi ko kehtey suna ke mainey Ahmed bin Hanbal sey Abdur-Rehman bin Zaid bin Aslam key barey mein poochha? to unhoney kaha : un ke bhai Abdullah bin Zaid bin Aslam mein koi harj nahin. 5- aur mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey suna ke Ali bin Abdullah Al Madeeni ne Abdullah bin Zaid bin Aslam bharosemand hain aur Abdur-Rehman bin Zaid bin Aslam zaeef hain padhi. Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : main unse kuchh riwayat nahin karta."
720,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisey qai aa jaey is par rozey ki qaza lazim nahin padhi. aur jo jaan boojh kar qai karey to usey rozey ki qaza karni chahiye.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum usey basanad (Hisham an ibne Sireen an Abi Huraira an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) Esa bin Yunus hi key tareeq sey jantey hain. Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : main isey mehfooz nahin samajhta. 3- ye hadees dusri aur sanadon sey bhi Abu-Hurera sey riwayat ki gaee hai aur unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai lekin iski sanad sahih nahin hai. 4- is bab mein Abu-Darda , Soban aur Fazala bin Ubaid (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 5- Abu-Darda , Soban aur Fazala bin Ubaid (Raziallauh anhum) sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney qai ki to aap ney roza tod diya. i ka matlab ye hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam nafli rozey sey they. qai hui to aap ney kuchh kamzori mehsus ki isliye roza tod diya, baaz riwayaat mein iski tafseer isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai. 6- aur ehle-ilm ka amal Abu-Hurera ki hadees par hai jisey unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai ke roze-daar ko jab qai aa jaey to is par qaza lazim nahin hai. aur jab qai jaan-bujh kar karey to usey chahiye ke qaza karey. Sufiyan Sory , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya isi ke qaail hain."
721,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney bhool kar kuch kha pi liya, wo roza na todey , ye rozi hai jo Allah ney isey di hai''."
722,"Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey usi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri aur Umme Is-haq Ghanviya Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- aksar ehle-ilm ka amal isi par hai. Sufiyan Sory , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya usi key qaail hain, 4- Malik bin Anas kehtey hain ke jab koi Ramzan mein bhool kar kha pi ley to is par rozon ki qaza lazim hai, pehla qol ziyada sahih hai."
723,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney baghair kisi sharae rukhsat aur baghair kisi bimari key Ramzan ka koi roza nahin rakha to purey saal ka roza bhi us ko pura nahin kar paeyga chahey wo purey saal rozey sey rahey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees ko hum sirf isi tareeq sey jantey hain, 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna ke abul-Mutwis ka naam Yazeed bin Mutwis hai aur uskey ilawa mujhey unki koi aur hadees malum nahin."
724,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik shakhs ney aa kar kaha : Allah key Rasool ! main halak ho gaya, aap ney puchha : ''tumhen kis chiz ney halak kar diya?'' usney arz kya : main Ramzan main apni biwi sey sohbat kar betha. aap ney puchha : '' kya tum eik ghulam ya laundi azad kar saktey ho?'' usney kaha : nahin, aap ney puchha : ''kya musalsal do maah key rozey rakh saktey ho?'' usney kaha : nahin, to aap ney puchha : ''kya saath miskeen ko khana khila saktey ho? '' usney kaha : nahin, to aap ney farmaya : '' beth jaao '' to wo beth gaya, itney mein aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik bada tokra laya gaya jis mein khajuren thin, aap ney farmaya : ''isey ley ja kar sadqa kar do'', usney arz kya : in dono miley huye ilaqon key darmiyan ki basti ( yani Madina mein) mujh sey ziyada mohtaj koi nahin hai. Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hans padey, yahan tak ke aap key samney key sath waley daant dikhai deney lagey, aap ney farmaya : ''isey ley lo aur ley ja kar apney ghar walon hi ko khila do''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar , Aaisha aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ka us shakhs key barey mein jo Ramzan mein jaan-bujh kar biwi sey jima kar key roza tod dey, isi hadees par amal hai, 4- aur jo jaan-bujh kar kha pi kar roza todey, to uskey barey mein ehle-ilm mein ikhtilaf hai. baaz kehtey hain : is par rozey ki qaza aur kaffara dono lazim hai, un logon ney khaney-peeney ko jima key mushabeh qarar diya hai. Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak aur Is-haq bin Raahviya isi key qaail hain. baaz kehtey hain is par sirf rozey ki qaza lazim hai, kaffara nahin . isliye ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey jo kaffara mazkur hai wo jima sey mutalliq hai, khaney peeney key barey mein aap sey kaffara mazkur nahin hai, un logon ney kaha hai ke khana-peena jima key mushabeh nahin hai. ye Shafai aur Ahmed ka qol hai. Shafai kehtey hain : Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka us shakhs sey jisney roza tod diya, aur aap ney is par sadqa kya ye kehna ke ''usey ley lo aur ley ja kar apney ghar walon hi ko khila do'', kaee baaton ka ehtimaal rakhta hai : eik ehtimaal ye bhi hai ke kaffara us shakhs par hoga jo is par qadir ho, aur ye aisa shakhs tha jisey kaffara deney ki qudrat nahin thi, to jab Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney isey kuch diya aur wo uska Malik ho gaya to us aadmi ney arz kya : hum sey ziyada uska koi mohtaj nahin, to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''usey ley lo aur ja kar apney ghar walon hi ko khila do'', isliye ke rozaana ki khurak sey bachney key baad hi kaffara lazim aata hai, to jo is tarah ki soorate-haal sey guzar raha ho uskey liye Shafai ney isi baat ko pasand kya hai ke wohi usey kha ley aur kaffara is par farz rahega, jab kabhi wo maaldaar hoga to kaffara ada kerega."
725,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko rozey ki haalat mein itni baar miswak kartey dekha ke main usey shumar nahin kar sakta . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aamir bin Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- isi hadees par ehle-ilm ka amal hai. ye log rozey daar key miswak karney mein koi harj nahin padhi. samajhtey, albatta baaz ehle-ilm ney rozey daar key liye tazi lakdi ki miswak ko makrooh qarar diya hai, aur din key aakhiri hissey mein bhi miswak ko makrooh kaha hai. lekin Shafai din key shuru ya aakhiri kisi bhi hissey mein miswak karney mein harj mehsus nahin kartey. Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ney din key aakhiri hissey mein miswak ko makrooh qarar diya hai."
726,"eik shakhs ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar puchha : meri aankh aa gaee hai, kya main surma laga lun , main rozey sey hun? aap ney farmaya : '' haan '' ( laga lo ( . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas ki hadees ki sanad qawi nahin hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi koi chiz sahih nahin, 3- abu-Aatika zaeef qarar diye jatey hain, 4- is bab mein abu-Raafey sey bhi riwayat hai, 5- Saaim key surma laganey mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai, baaz ney isey makrooh qarar diya hai padhi. ye Sufiyan Sory, ibne-Mubarak, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai aur baaz ehle-ilm ney roza daar ko surma laganey ki rukhsat di hai aur ye Shafai ka qol hai."
727,"Hazrat Aaeysha farmaati hain ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam maah siyaam ( Ramzan ( mein bosa letey they padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein umr bin Khattab , Hafsa , abu Saeed Khudri , Umme-Salma , ibne-Abbas , Anas aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- rozedar key bosa leney key silsiley mein Sahaba kiram waghaira ka ikhtilaf hai. baaz Sahaba ney boodhey key liye bosa leney ki rukhsat di hai. aur nojawanon key liye is andeshey key peshe-nazar rukhsat nahin di ke uska saum mehfooz o maamoon nahin reh sakeyga. jima unkey nazdik ziyada sakht chiz hai. baaz ehle-ilm ney kaha hai : bosa ajr kam kar deta hai lekin us sey rozedaar ka roza nahin toot-ta , unka khayal hai ke rozedaar ko agar apney nafs par qabu ( kantrol (ho to wo bosa ley sakta hai aur jab wo apney aap par kantrol na rakh sakey to bosa na ley taake uska roza mehfooz o maamoon rahey, ye Sufiyan Sory aur Shafai ka qol hai."
728,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam rozey ki haalat mein mujh sey bos-o-kinaar kartey they, aap apni khaahish par tum mein sab sey ziyada kantrol rakhney waley they."
729,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam rozey ki haalat mein bosa letey aur apni biwiyon key sath lipat kar let'tey they, aap apni jinsi khaahish par tum mein sab sey ziyada kantrol rakhney waley they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. - aur « لإربه » key maana « لنفسه » '' apney nafs par '' key hain."
730,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney rozey ki niyat Fajr sey pehley nahin kar li , uska roza nahin huwa '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Hafsa (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees ko hum sirf isi sanad sey marfoo jantey hain, neez usey Nafey sey bhi riwayat kya gaya hai unhoney ibne-Umar sey riwayat ki hai aur usey ibne-Umar hi ka qol qarar diya hai, uska maqoof hona hi ziyada sahih hai, aur isi tarah ye hadees Zohri sey bhi moqufan marvi hai, hum nahin jantey ke kisi ney isey marfoo kya hai Yahya bin Ayub key siwa, 2- iska maana ehle-ilm key nazdik sirf ye hai ke uska roza nahin hota, jo Ramzan mein ya Ramzan ki qaza mein ya nazar key rozey mein rozey ki niyat tulu Fajr sey pehley nahin karta. agar usney raat mein niyat nahin ki to uska roza nahin huwa, albatta nafl rozey mein uskey liye subh ho janey key baad bhi rozey ki niyat karna mubaah hai. yehi Shafai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai."
731,"main Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas bethi hui thi, itney mein aap key paas peeney ki koi chiz laee gaee , aap ney is mein sey piya , phir mujhey diya to mainey bhi piya . phir mainey arz kya : mainey gunah ka kaam kar liya hai. aap merey liye bakhshish ki dua kar dijiye . aap ney puchha : '' kya baat hai? ''main ney kaha : main rozey sey thi aur mainey roza tod diya to aap ney puchha : '' kya koi qaza ka roza tha jisey tum qaza kar rahi thi ?'' arz kya : nahin, aap ney farmaya : ''to us sey tumhen koi nuqsan honey wala nahin''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein abu Saeed Khudri aur ummul-momenin Aaisha Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
732,"Umme-Haani (Raziallahu Anha) key dono beton mein sey eik ney mujh sey hadees bayan ki to main un dono mein jo sab sey afzal tha us sey mila , uska naam Ja'ada tha, Umme-Haani uski daadi thin, usney mujh sey bayan kiya ke uski daadi kehti hain ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam unke yahaan aaye to aap ney koi peeney ki chiz mangaai aur usey piya. phir aap ney unhen diya to unhoney bhi piya. phir unhoney puchha : Allah key Rasool ! main to rozey sey thi. to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''nafl roza rakhney wala apney nafs ka ameen hai, chahey to roza rakhey aur chahey to na rakhey.'' Shoba kehtey hain : mainey Simaak sey puchha : kya aap ney isey Umme-Haani sey suna hai? kaha : nahin, mujhey Abu-Saaleh ney aur hamarey ghar walon ney khabar di hai aur un logon ney Umme-Haani sey riwayat ki. Hammad bin Salma ney bhi ye hadees Sumaak bin Harab sey riwayat ki hai. is mein hai Umme-Haani ki ladki key betey Harun sey riwayat hai, unhoney Umme-Haani sey riwayat ki hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Shoba ki riwayat sab sey behtar hai, isi tarah hum sey Mehmood bin Ghelaan ney bayan kiya hai aur Mehmood ney Abu-Daawood sey riwayat ki hai, is mein (Ameen apne liye) hai. albatta Abu-Daawood sey Mehmood key ilawa doosrey logon ney jo riwayat ki to un logon ney (Ameer apne liye ya Ameen apne liye) shak key sath kaha. aur isi tarah Shoba sey mutaaddid (bahutsi) sanadon sey bhi (Ameer apne liye ya Ameen apne liye) shak key sath waarid hai. Umme-Haani ki hadees ki sanad mein kalam hai. 2- aur Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke nafl roza rakhney wala agar roza tod dey to is par koi qaza lazim nahin siwaye iske ke wo qaza karna chahey. yehi Sufiyan Sory, Ahmed , Is-haq bin Raahviya aur Shafai ka qol hai."
733,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam eik din merey paas aaye aur aap ney puchha : ''kya tumharey paas kuchh (khaney ko) hai.'' mainey arz kya : nahin, to aap ney farmaya : ''to main rozey sey hun.''"
734,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam merey paas aatey to poochhtey : ''kya tumharey paas khana hai?'' main kehti : nahin. to aap farmatey : ''to main rozey sey hun.''  eik din aap merey paas tashrif laye to mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! hamarey paas eik hadiya aaya hai. aap ney puchha : ''kya chiz hai?'' mainey arz kiya : ''hees''  aap ney farmaya : ''main subah sey rozey sey hun''  phir aap ney kha liya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
735,"Main aur Hafsa dono rozey sey thin, hamarey paas khaney ki eik chiz aai jiski hamein raghbat (dilchaspi) hui, to hamney is mein sey kha liya. itney mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aagey , to Hafsa mujh sey sabqat kar gaeen. wo apney baap hi ki beti to thin. unhoney puchha : Allah key Rasool ! hum log rozey sey they. hamarey samney khana aa gaya, to hamein uski khahish hui to hamney isey kha liya , aap ney farmaya : ''tum dono kisi aur din iski qaza kar lena.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Saleh bin Abi Akhzar aur Muhammad bin abi Hafsa ney ye hadees basanad (Zohri an Urwa an Aaisha) isi key jaisi riwayat ki hai. aur isey Malik bin Anas , Maamar , Ubedullah bin umr , Ziyad bin Saad aur doosrey kaee Haafizon ney basanad (Zohri an Aaisha) mursalan riwayat ki hai aur un logon ney is mein Urwa key wastey ka zikr nahin kiya hai, aur yehi ziyada sahih hai. isliye ke ibne-Jurej sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke mainey Zohri sey puchha : kya aap sey isey Urwa ney bayan kiya aur Urwa sey Aaisha ney riwayat ki hai? to unhoney kaha : mainey is silsiley mein Urwa sey koi chiz nahin suni hai. mainey Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Abdul-Malik ke ehad khilaafat mein baaz aisey logon sey suna hai jinhoney aisey shakhs sey riwayat ki hai jisney is hadees key barey mein Aaisha sey poochha. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat isi hadees ki taraf gaee hai. un logon ka kehna hai ke koi nafl roza tod dey to is par qaza lazim hai padhi. Malik bin Anas ka yehi qol hai."
736,"Mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko lagatar do mahinon key rozey rakhtey nahin dekha siwaye Shoban padhi. aur Ramzan key . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- aur ye hadees abu-Salma sey ba-riwayat Aaisha bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai wo kehti hain ke mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko Shoban sey ziyada kisi mahiney mein rozey rakhtey nahin dekha, aap Shoban key sarey rozey rakhtey , siwaye chand dino key balke purey hi Shoban rozey rakhtey they."
737,"Isey Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kiya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin Mubarak is hadees ke barey mein kehtey hain ke kalame-arab mein ye jayez hai ke jab koi mahiney ke aksar dinon (din) roza rakhey to kaha jaey ke usney purey mahiney key rozey rakhey, aur kaha jaey ke usne puri raat namaz padhi halanke usne Sham ka khana bhi khaya aur baaz doosrey kamon mein bhi mashghool raha۔ goya ibne-Mubarak dono hadeeson ko eik doosrey ke muwaafiq samajhtey hain. is tarah is hadees ka mafhoom ye hua ke aap is mahiney ke aksar dinon (din) mein roza rakhtey they. 2- Salim Abu Nazar aur doosrey kaee logon ney bhi ba-tareeq Abu-Salma an Aaisha Muhammad bin Amr ki tarah riwayat ki hai."
738,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab aadha Shoban reh jaey to roza na rakho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. hum isey in alfaz ke sath sirf isi tareeq sey jantey hain. 2- aur is hadees ka mafhoom baaz ehle-ilm ke nazdik ye hai ke aadmi pehley sey roza na rakh raha ho, phir jab Shoban khatam honey ke kuchh din baqi reh jaeyn to maahe Ramzan ki tazeem (izzat) mein roza rakhna shuru kar dey. isi ke saath Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey wo cheezen riwayat ki hai jo un logon ke qol sey milta julta hai jaisa ke aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''maahe-Ramzan ke istaqbal mein pehley sey roza na rakho'' siwaye iskey ke in dinon (dinon) mein koi aisa roza pad jaey jisey tum pehley sey rakhtey aa rahey ho. ye hadees is baat par dalalat karti hai ke karaahat us shakhs key liye hai jo jaan bujh-kar Ramzan ki tazeem mein roza rakhey."
739,"Mainey eik raat Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko ghaaieb paya . to main (aap ki talash mein) bahar nikli to kya dekhti hun ke aap Baqee qabristaan mein hain. aap ney farmaya : ''kya tum dar rahi thi ke Allah aur uskey Rasool tum par zulm karengey.'' mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! mera guman tha ke aap apni kisi biwi key yahaan gaey hongey. aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala pandrahwin Shoban padhi. ki raat ko aasmane-duniya par nuzool farmata hai, aur qabila kalb ki bakriyon ke baalon sey ziyada tadaad mein logon ki maghfirat farmata hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees ko hum is sanad sey sirf Hujjaaj ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko is hadees ki zaeef thehrartey suna hai, isi ke saath farmaya : Yahya bin Abi Kasir ko Urwa sey aur Hujjaaj bin Irtaat ko Yahya bin Abi Kasir sey nahin suna hai. 3- is bab mein abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
740,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''maahe Ramzan key baad sab sey afzal roza Allah key mahiney padhi. mohrram ka roza hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai.
741,"eik shakhs ney unse puchha : maahe-Ramzan key baad kis mahiney mein roza rakhney ka aap mujhey hukm detey hain? to unhoney us sey kaha : mainey is silsiley mein siwaye eik shakhs key kisi ko poochhtey nahin suna , mainey usey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey sawal kartey suna , aur main aap key paas hi betha huwa tha. usne puchha : Allah key Rasool ! maahe Ramzan ke baad aap mujhey kis mahiney mein roza rakhney ka hukm detey hain? aap ney farmaya : ''agar maahe Ramzan ke baad tumhen roza rakhna hi ho to mohrram ka roza rakho , wo Allah ka mahina hai. is main eik din aisa hai jis mein Allah ney kuchh logon par rehmat ki padhi. aur is mein doosrey logon par bhi rehmat karega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
742,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam har maah key shuru key teen din rozey rakhtay. aur aisa kam hota tha ke Jume ke din aap roze sey na hon. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Shoba ney ye hadees Aasim sey riwayat ki hai aur isey marfoo nahin kiya 3- is bab mein ibne-Umar aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 4- ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat ney Jume key din roza rakhney ko mustahab qarar diya hai. makrooh ye hai ke aadmi sirf Jume ko roza rakhey na is se pehley rakhey aur na iskey baad.
743,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum mein sey koi Jume key din roza na rakhey, illa ye ke wo is sey pehley ya uskey baad bhi roza rakhey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali , Jabir , Junaada Azdi , Juweriya , Anas aur Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. ye log aadmi ke liye makrooh samajhtey hain ke wo Jume key din ko roze ke liye makhsus kar ley, na is sey pehley roza rakhey aur na uskey baad۔ Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain."
744,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''hafte key din roza mat rakho padhi. , siwaye uskey ke jo Allah ney tum par farz kiya ho, agar tum mein sey koi angoor ki chhaal aur darkht ki tehni key ilawa kuchh na paey to usi ko chabaa ley (aur roza na rakhey). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- aur iskey makrooh honey ka matlab ye hai ke aadmi roze key liye haftey (saneechar) ka din makhsus kar ley, isliye ke Yahudi haftey ke din ki tazeem (izzat) kartey hain."
745,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Somwar aur Jumerat key rozey ki talash mein rehtey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan hai aur is sanad sey gharib hai.
746,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam eik mahina hafta (saneechar), itwaar aur Somwar ko aur doosrey mahine mangal , buddh , aur Jumerat ko roza rakhtey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- Abdur-Rehman bin Mehdi ney is hadees ko Sufiyan sey riwayat kiya hai aur isey marfoo nahin kiya hai."
747,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''somwaar (peer)  aur Jumerat ko aamal (Allah key huzur) pesh kiye jatey hain, meri khahish hai ke mera amal us haal mein pesh kiya jaey ke main rozey sey hun.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees is baab mein Hasan gharib hai."
748,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey saal bhar ke rozon ke barey mein poochha, ya aap sey saal bhar ke rozon ke baarey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : ''tum par tumharey ghar walon ka bhi haq hai, Ramzan ke rozey rakho, aur us mahiney ke rakho jo is sey muttasil (lage hue) hai, aur har buddh aur Jumerat key rozey rakho , jab tum ney ye rozey rakh liye , to ab goya tum ney saal bhar roze rakhe aur iftaar kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Muslim Qurshi (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees gharib hai. 2- baaz logon ney ba-tareeq (Harun bin Salman an Muslim bin Ubedullah an Ubedullah bin Muslim) riwayat ki hai. 3- is bab mein Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
749,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main Allah Taala sey ummid rakhta hun ke Arfa key din padhi. ka roza eik saal pehley aur eik saal baad key gunah mita dega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- ehle-ilm ney Arfa ke din ke rozey ko mustahab qarar diya hai, magar jo log Arafat mein hon unke liye mustahab nahin."
750,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Arafat mein roza nahin rakha , Umme Fazal (Raziallahu Anha) ney aap key paas doodh bheja to aap ney isey piya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , ibne-Umar aur Umme Fazal (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath Haj kiya to aap ney us din ka (yani Arfa ke din ka ( roza nahin rakha aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key sath Haj kiya to unhoney bhi isey nahin rakha, umr key sath Haj kiya, to unhoney bhi isey nahin rakha, aur Usman key sath Haj kya to unhoney bhi isey nahin rakha. 4- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. ye log Arafat mein roza na rakhney ko mustahab samajhtey hain taake aadmi dua ki ziyada sey ziyada qudrat rakh sakey. 5- aur baaz ehle-ilm ney Arfa key din Arafat mein roza rakha hai."
751,"Ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey Arfa key din Arafat mein roza rakhney key barey mein puchha gaya to unhoney kaha ke mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath Haj kiya. aap ney us din ka roza nahin rakha. abu-Bakar key sath Haj kiya, unhoney bhi nahin rakha , umr key sath kiya. unhoney bhi nahin rakha. Usman key sath kiya to unhoney bhi nahin rakha (Raziallauh anhum), main bhi us din (wahan Arafat mein) roza nahin rakhta hun, albatta na to main iska hukm deta hun aur na hi is sey rokta hun. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- ye hadees ibne-Abi Najeeh sey ba-tareeq : (an Abeeh an Rajul an ibne-Umar) bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai. Abu Najih ka naam Yasar hai aur unhoney ibne-Umar sey suna hai."
752,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main Allah sey ummid rakhta hun ke Aashuraa key din ka roza eik saal pehley key gunah mita dega.''Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Ali , Muhammad bin Saifi, Salma bin Akwaa, Hind bin Asmaa, ibne-Abbas, Rabee binte Muawwiz bin Ifra , Abdur-Rehman bin Salma Khuza'ee, jinhoney apney chacha sey riwayat ki hai aur Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Aashuraa key din key roza rakhney par ubhaaraa. 2- Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees key ilawa hum nahin jantey ke kisi aur riwayat mein aap ney ye farmaya ho ke Aashuraa key din ka roza eik saal key gunahon ka kaffara hai. Ahmed aur Is-haq ka qol bhi Abu-Qatada ki hadees ke mutabiq hai."
753,"Aashuraa eik aisa din tha ke jis mein Quraish zamanae-jahiliyat mein roza rakhtey they aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam bhi us din roza rakhtey they, jab aap Madina aaye to us din aap ney roza rakha aur logon ko bhi us din roza rakhney ka hukm diya, lekin jab Ramzan key rozey farz kiye gaey to sirf Ramzan hi key rozey farz rahey aur aap ney Aashuraa ka roza tarak kar diya, to jo chahey is din roza rakhey aur jo chahey na rakhey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai padhi. , padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood , Qais bin Saad , Jabir bin Samura , ibne-Umar aur Muawiya (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm ka amal Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees par hai, aur ye hadees sahih hai, ye log Aashuraa ke din ke rozey ko wajib nahin samajhtey, siwaaye iske ke jo iski us fazilat ki wajeh sey jo zikr ki gaee uski raghbat (dilchaspi) rakhey."
754,"Main ibne-Abbas ke paas pahuncha , wo zamzam par apni chadar ka takiya lagaey huye they, mainey puchha : mujhey Aashuraa ke din ke barey mein bataiye ke wo kon sa din hai jis mein main roza rakhun? unhoney kaha : jab tum mohrram ka chaand dekho to din gino, aur naween taareekh ko roza rakh kar subah karo. mainey puchha : kya isi tarah sey Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam rakhtey they? kaha : haan (isi tarah rakhtey they)."
755,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney daswin taareekh ko Aashuraa ka roza rakhney ka hukm diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ehle-ilm ka Aashuraa ke din ke silsiley mein ikhtilaf hai. baaz kehtey hain : Aashuraa nawan din hai aur baaz kehtey hain : daswaan din padhi. ibne-Abbas sey marvi hai ke naween aur daswin din ka roza rakho aur yahudiyon ki mukhalifat karo. Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol isi hadees ke mutabiq hai."
756,Mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko zil-hijja ke das dino mein rozey rakhtey kabhi nahin dekha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- isi tarah kaee doosrey logon ney bhi ba-tareeq (الأعمش an إبراهيم an الأسود an عائشة ) riwayat ki hai. 2- aur Sauri waghera ney ye hadees b-tareeq ( منصور an ابراہیم النخعی ) yun riwayat ki hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko zil-hijja key das dino mein roza rakhtey nahin dekha gaya. 3- aur Abul Ahwas ney ba-tareeq(Mansoor an Ibrahim Al Nakhaee an Aaisha) riwayat ki is mein unhoney Aswad key wastey ka zikr nahin kiya hai. 4- aur logon ney is hadees mein Mansoor par ikhtilaf kiya hai. aur Aamash ki riwayat ziyada sahih hai aur sanad ke aetbar sey sab sey ziyada muttasil hai. 5- Aamash Ibrahim Nakhai ki sanad ke Mansoor sey ziyada yad rakhney waley.
757,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''zil-hijja ke das dino ke muqabley mein doosrey koi dinon (din) aisey nahin jin mein nek amal Allah ko in dino sey ziyada mehbub hon.''  logon ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! Allah ki raah mein jihad karna bhi nahin? aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah ki raah mein jihad karna bhi nahin, siwaye us Mujahid key jo apni jaan aur maal dono ley kar Allah ki raah mein nikla phir kisi chiz key sath wapis nahin aaya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar , Abu-Hurera , Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
758,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''zil-hijja key (ibtidaai) das dino sey badh kar koi din aisa nahin jiski ibadat Allah ko ziyada mehbub ho, in dinon (dinon) mein sey har din ka roza saal bhar key rozon ke barabar hai aur in ki har raat ka qiyam lailatul-qadr ke qiyam ke barabar hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf Masood bin Wasil ki hadees sey is tareeq ke ilawa jantey hain aur Masood ney Nahhaas sey riwayat ki hai. 3- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is hadees ke barey mein puchha to wo isey kisi aur tareeq sey nahin jaan sakey. 4- is mein sey kuchh jisey Qatada ney basanad (قتادة an سعيد بن المسيب an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم ) mursalan riwayat ki hai. 4- Yahya bin Saeed ney Nahhaas bin Qaham par in ke haafze ke talluq sey kalam kiya hai."
759,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney Ramzan key rozey rakhey phir uskey baad shawwaal key chhe (nafli) rozey rakhey to yehi saume-dahar (pure saal roze rakhna) hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Abdul-Azeez bin Muhammad ney is hadees ko b-tareeq : (Safwaan bin Saleem bin Saeed an umr bin Sabit an abi Ayyoob an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat kiya hai. 3- Shoba ney ye hadees b-tareeq : (Warqaa bin umr an Saad bin Saeed) riwayat ki hai, Saad bin Saeed , Yahya bin Saeed Ansari ke bhai hain. 4- baaz muhaddeseen ney Saad bin Saeed par haafze ke aetbar sey kalam kiya hai. 5- Hasan Basri sey riwayat hai ke jab unkey paas shawwaal key chhe din key rozon ka zikr kiya jata to wo kehtey : Allah ki qism , Allah Taala is maah key rozon sey purey saal razi hai. 6- is bab mein Jabir , Abu-Hurera aur Soban (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 7- eik jamaat ney is hadees ki taraf sey shawwaal ke chhe din key rozon ko mustahab kaha hai. 8- ibne-Mubarak kehtey hain : ye achchha hai, ye har maah teen din key rozon key jaise hain. 9- ibne-Mubarak kehtey hain : baaz hadeeson mein marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke ye rozey Ramzan sey mila diye jaeyn. 10 - aur ibne-Mubarak ney pasand kya hai ke ye rozey mahiney key ibtidaai chhe dino mein hon. 11 - ibne-Mubarak ney ye bhi kaha : agar koi shawwaal ke chhe din ke rozey alag alag dino mein rakhe to ye bhi jayez hai."
760,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujh sey teen baaton ka ehad liya : 1- main witr padhey baghair na so'un. 2- har maah teen din key rozey rakhun. 3- aur chaasht ki namaz padha karun.
761,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Abu-Zar ! jab tum har maah key teen din key rozey rakho to terhiwin, chaudahween aur pandrahwin taareekh ko rakho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Qatada , Abdullah bin Amr , Qurra bin Ayas Muzni , Abdullah bin Masood , Abu Aqrab, ibne-Abbas , Aaisha , Qatada bin Milhaan, Usman bin Abi Al-Aas aur Jareer (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- baaz hadeeson mein ye bhi hai ke ''jisney har maah teen din key rozey rakhey to wo us shakhs ki tarah hai jisney pure saal roze rakhe hon.''"
762,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney har maah teen din key rozey rakhey to yehi saume-dahar (pure saal roze rakhna) hai.''  iski tasdeeq Allah Taala ney apni kitab mein nazil farmaee irshad Baari hai : ''jisney eik neki ki to usey (kam sey kam) is ka das guna ajr milega'' (Al inaam -190) goya eik din ( kam sey kam ( das din key barabar hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Shoba ney ye hadees ba-tareeq : (أبي شمر وأبي التياح an أبي عثمان an أبي هريرة an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) riwayat ki hai.
763,"Mainey Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey puchha : kya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam har maah teen rozey rakhtey they? to unhoney kaha : haan rakhtey they, mainey kaha : kon si taareekhon mein rakhtey they? kaha : aap is baat ki parwah nahin kartey they ke kon si taareekh hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Yazeed Rashk Yazeed Zab'ee hi hain, yehi Yazeed bin Qasim bhi hain aur yehi Qassam hain, Rashk key maana ehale Basra ki lughat mein Qassam ke hain."
764,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tumhara rab farmata hai : har neki ka badla das guna sey ley kar saat-sau guna tak hai. aur roza merey liye hai aur main hi uska badla dunga. roza jahannam key liye dhaal hai, roze-daar ke munh ki boo Allah key nazdik mushk ki khushbu sey ziyada pakizah hai, aur agar tum mein sey koi jahil kisi key sath jihalat sey pesh aaye aur wo rozey sey ho to usey keh dena chahiye ke main rozey sey hun.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Muaz bin Jabal , Sehal bin Saad , Kaab bin Ajra , Sulaama bin Qaisar aur Bashir bin Khasaasiya (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Bashir ka naam Zaham bin Maabad hai aur Khasaasiya in ki maa hain."
765,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jannat main eik darwaza hai jisey Rayyaan kaha jata hai. roza rakhney walon padhi. ko uski taraf bulaya jaeyga, to jo roze rakhney walon mein sey hoga is mein dakhil ho jaeyga aur jo is mein dakhil ho gaya, wo kabhi piyasa nahin hoga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
766,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''roze-daar ke liye do khushiyan hain : eik khushi iftaar kartey waqt hoti hai aur dusri us waqt hogi jab wo apney rab sey milega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
767,"Arz kiya gaya : Allah key Rasool ! agar koi saume-dahar (purey saal rozey) rakhey to kaisa hai? aap ney farmaya : ''us ney na roza rakha aur na hi iftaar kiya.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Qatada ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin umr , Abdullah bin Shikhkhir , Imran bin Husain aur abu-Musa (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat ney saume-dahar (purey saal rozey) ko makrooh kaha hai aur baaz doosrey logon ney isey jayez qarar diya hai. wo kehtey hain ke saume-dahar (purey saal rozey) to us waqt hoga jab Eidul-Fitr, Eidul-Azha aur tashreeq wale dinon mein bhi roza rakhna na chhodey, jisney un dino mein roza tarak kar diya, wo karaahat ki had sey nikal gaya, aur wo purey saal roza rakhney wala nahin huwa Malik bin Anas sey isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai aur yehi Shafai ka bhi qol hai. Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi isi tarah kehtey hain, un dono ka kehna hai ke in paanch dino yani donon Eidon aur tashreeq ke dinon mein roza rakhney sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mana farmaya hai, baqiya dino mein iftaar karna wajib nahin hai."
768,"Mainey Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key rozon key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam roza rakhtey yahan tak ke hum kehtey ke aap ney khub rozey rakhey , phir aap rozey rakhna chhod detey yahan tak ke hum kehtey ke aap ney bahut dino sey roze nahin rakhey. aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ne Ramzan ke ilawa kisi maah ke purey rozey nahin rakhey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Anas aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
769,"un sey Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key rozon key barey mein sawal kiya gaya to unhoney kaha : aap kisi mahiney mein itney rozey rakhtey ke hum samajhtey : ab aap ka irada rozey band karney ka nahin hai, aur kabhi baghair rozey key rehtey yahan tak ke hamein khayal hota ke aap koi roza rakhengey hi nahin. aur aap ko raat key jis hissey mein bhi tum namaz padhta dekhna chahtey namaz padhtey dekh letey aur jis hissey mein sotey huye dekhna chahtey to sotey huye dekh letey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
770,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sab sey afzal roza merey bhai Dawud (Alaihissalam) ka roza hai, wo eik din roza rakhtey they aur eik din baghair roze key rehtey, aur jab (dushman sey) mudbhed hoti to maidan chhod kar bhagtey nahin they.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke sab sey afzal roza ye hai ke tum eik din roza rakho aur eik din baghair roze key raho , kaha jata hai ke ye sab sey sakht roza hai."
771,"Main umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) key paas daswen zil-hijja ko mojud tha, unhoney khutbey sey pehley namaz shuru ki, phir kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko in do dino mein roza rakhney sey mana farmatey suna hai, eidul-Fitr key din sey, isliye ke ye tumharey rozon sey iftaar ka din aur musalmanon ki Eid hai aur Eidul-Azha key din isliye ke us din tum apni qurbaaniyon ka gosht khaao. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
772,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney do rozon sey mana farmaya : ''Eidul-Azha (Baqar-eid) ke din ke rozey sey aur Eidul-Fitr ke din ke rozey sey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein umr , Ali , Aaisha , Abu-Hurera , Aqba bin Aamir aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. 4- Amr bin Yahya hi Umaara bin abi Hasan Mazni hain, wo Madiney key rehney waley hain aur bharosemand hain. Sufiyan Sory , Shoba aur Malik bin Anas ney in sey hadisein riwayat ki hain."
773,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Arfa ke din, nahar (qurbani) ke din aur  tashreeq ke dinon mein  hamari yani ehale Islam ki Eid key din hain, aur ye khaney peeney key din hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali , Saad , Abu-Hurera , Jabir , Nabeesha , Bishr bin Saheem, Abdullah bin Huzaafa , Anas , Hamza bin Amr Aslami , Kaab bin Malik , Aaisha , Amr bin al-Aas aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. ye log tashreeq ke dino mein roza rakhney ko haram qarar detey hain. albatta Sahaba kiram waghaira ki eik jamaat ney Haj tamatto karney waley ko uski rukhsat (chhoot) di hai jab wo buraai na paey aur usney zil-hijja key ibtidaai das din mein roze na rakhey hon ke wo  tashreeq ke dino mein roza rakhey. Malik bin Anas , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi isi ke qaail hain."
774,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''seengi (pachhnaa) laganey aur lagwaaney waley dono ka roza nahin raha.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Raafey bin khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Ahmed bin Hanbal kehtey hain ke is baab mein sab sey sahih Raafey bin khadij ki riwayat hai, 3- aur Ali bin Abdullah (ibne-Madeeni) kehtey hain ke is baab mein sab sey sahih Soban aur Shaddad bin Auski hadisein hain, isliye ke Yahya bin abi Kasir ney Abu-Qulaba sey Soban aur Shaddad bin Aus dono ki hadeeson ki eik sath riwayat ki hai. 4- is bab mein Ali , Saad , Shaddad bin Aus 'Soban' Usama bin Zaid , Aaisha , Maaqil bin Sanan (ibne Yasar bhi kaha jata hai), Abu-Hurera , ibne-Abbas , Abu-Musa , Bilal aur Saad (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 5- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ney roze-daar key liye pachhna lagwaaney ko makrooh qarar diya hai, yahan tak ke baaz Sahaba ney raat ko pachhna lagwaayaa. in mein Musa Ash-ari , aur ibne-Umar bhi hain. ibne-Mubarak bhi yehi kehtey hain : 6- Abdur-Rehman bin Mehdi kehtey hain ke jisney rozey ki haalat mein pachhna lagwaayaa , is par uski qaza hai, Is-haq bin Mansoor kehtey hain : isi tarah Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ney bhi kaha hai, 7- Shafai kehtey hain ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke aap ney rozey ki haalat mein pachhna lagwaayaa. aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke aap ney farmaya : ''pachhnaa laganey aur lagwaaney waley dono ney roza tod diya.'' aur main un dono hadeeson mein sey eik bhi sahih nahin jaanta , lekin agar koi roze ki haalat mein pachhna lagwaaney sey ijtinab (parhez) karey to ye mujhey ziyada mehbub hai, aur agar koi roze-daar pachhna lagwa ley to main nahin samajhta ke us sey uska roza toot gaya. 8- Bagdaad mein Shafai ka bhi yehi qol tha ke is sey roza toot jata hai. albatta Misr mein wo rukhsat (chhoot) ki taraf maael ho gaey they aur roze-daar ke pachhna lagwaaney mein koi harj nahin samajhtey they. un ki daleel ye thi ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hajjatul-wadaa mein ehraam ki haalat mein pachhna lagwaayaa tha."
775,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney pachhna lagwaayaa , aap mohrim (ehraam ki haalat mein shakhs) they aur rozey sey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai. 2- isi tarah Wuhaib ney bhi Abdul-Waaris ki tarah riwayat ki hai. 3- Ismail bin Ibrahim bin Aleh ney Ayub sey aur Ayub ney Ikrima sey mursalan riwayat ki hai aur , Ikrima ney is mein ibne-Abbas ka zikr nahin kiya hai."
776,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney pachhna lagwaayaa , aap rozey sey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai."
777,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aisey waqt mein pachhna lagwaayaa jis mein aap Makka aur Madina key darmiyan they, aap ehraam baandhey huye they aur rozey ki haalat mein they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri , Jabir aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm isi hadees ki taraf gaey hain, wo roze-daar key pachhna lagwaaney mein koi harj nahin samajhtey. Sufiyan Sory , Malik bin Anas , aur Shafai ka bhi yehi qol hai."
778,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''saum-wisaal (lagatar roze)  mat rakho'' ,logon ney arz kiya : aap to rakhtey hain? Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : ''main tumhari tarah nahin hun. mera rab mujhey khilata pilata hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali , Abu-Hurera , Aaisha , ibne-Umar , Jabir , abu Saeed Khudri , aur Bashir bin Khsaasiya (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo baghair iftaar kiye lagatar rozey rakhney ko makrooh kehtey hain. 4- Abdullah bin Zuber Raziallahu anhuma sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke wo kaee dino ko mila letey they (darmiyan mein) iftaar nahin kartey they."
779,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko Fajr paa leti aur apni biwiyon sey sohbat ki wajeh sey haalate janabat (shohar biwi ki hambistari ke baad napaaki ki haalat) mein hotey phir aap ghusl farmatey aur roza rakhtey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain 1ـ :  Aaisha aur Umme-Salma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. Sufiyan , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai aur Tabe-een ki eik jamaat kehti hai ke jab koi haalate janabat (shohar biwi ki hambistari ke baad napaaki ki haalat) mein subah karey to wo us din ki qaza karey lekin pehla qol ziyada sahih hai."
780,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum mein sey kisi ko khaney ki dawat miley to usey qubul karey , aur agar wo roze sey ho to chahiye ke dua kerey.''"
781,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum mein sey kisi ko dawat di jaey aur wo roze sey ho to chahiye ke wo kahey mein roze sey hun.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Abu-Hurera sey marvi (riwayat hui) dono hadisein Hasan sahih hain.
782,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aurat apney shohar ki mojudgi mein maahe Ramzan key ilawa koi aur roza baghair uski ijazat key na rakhey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas aur abu-Saeed (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
783,Ramzan key jo rozey mujh par reh jatey unhe main Shoban hi mein qaza kar paati thi. jab tak ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wafat nahin ho gaee. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
784,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''roze-daar key paas jab iftaar ki cheezen khai jati hain, to farishtey uskey liye maghfirat ki dua kartey hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Shoba ney bhi ye hadees ba-tareeq : (حبيب بن زيد an ليلى an جدته أم عمارة an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم ) sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai. (jo aagey aa rahi hai.)"
785,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam unke paas aaye, unhoney aap ko khana pesh kiya, to aap ney farmaya : ''tum bhi khaao'' ,unhoney kaha : main roze se hun to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''roze-daar key liye farishtey istighfar kartey rehtey hain, jab uskey paas khaya jata hai jab tak ke khaney waley farigh na ho jaeyn.'' baaz riwaayaton mein hai ''jab tak ke wo aasooda (ranjeeda) na ho jaeyn.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aur ye Shareek ki (oopper wali) hadees sey ziyada sahih hai."
786,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai is mein (حتى يفرغوا أو يشبعوا ) ka zikr nahin hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Umme Imaara Habib bin Zaid Ansari ki daadi hain.
787,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney mein hamein haiz aata phir hum pak ho jatey to aap hamein rozey qaza karney ka hukm detey aur namaz qaza karney ka hukm nahin detey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- ye Muaaza sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai unhoney Aaisha sey riwayat ki hai. 3- aur isi par ehle-ilm ka amal hai, hum inke darmiyan is baat mein koi ikhtilaf nahin jantey ke haaiza aurat rozey ki qaza kareygi, namaz ki nahin kareygi."
788,"Mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! mujhey wuzu key barey mein bataiye . aap ney farmaya : ''kamil tareeqey sey wuzu karo, ungliyon key darmiyan Khilal karo aur naak mein pani chadhaane mein mubaalgha karo, siwaye iske ye ke tum rozey sey ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ehle-ilm ney roze-daar key liye naak mein pani chadhaane mubaalgha karney ko makrooh kaha hai. wo kehtey hain ke is sey roza toot jata hai. 3- is bab mein dusri riwayaat bhi hain jin sey inke qol ki taqwiyat (mazbooti) hoti hai."
789,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo kisi jamaat ke yahaan utrey yani unka mehman ho to unki ijazat ke baghair nafli rozey na rakhey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees munkir hai. 2- hum Siqaat mein sey kisi ko nahin jantey jisney ye hadees Hisham bin Urwa sey riwayat ki ho. 3- Musa bin Dawud ney ye hadees ba-tareeq : (abi Bakar Madeeni an Hisham bin Urwaa an Abeeh an Aaysha an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam) isi tarah riwayat ki hai. 4- ye hadees bhi zaeef hai, abu-Bakar ehle-hadees key nazdik zaeef hain, aur abu-Bakar madni jo Jabir bin Abdullah sey riwayat kartey hain, unka naam Fazal bin Mubashshir hai, wo inse ziyada bharosemand aur inse pehley key hain."
790,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Ramzan key aakhiri ashrey mein aetikaf padhi. kartey they, yahan tak ke Allah ney aap ko wafat di. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera aur Aaisha ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ubai-bin Kaab , abu-Leila , abu-Saeed , Anas aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
791,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab aetikaf ka irada kartey to Fajr padhtey phir apney moa'takif  (aetikaf ki jagah ( mein dakhil ho jatey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Yahya bin Saeed sey ba-wasta umra mursalan bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai (is mein Aaisha key wastey ka zikr nahin).  2- aur isey Malik aur deegar kaee logon ney Yahya bin Saeed sey aur Yahya ney umra sey mursalan hi riwayat ki hai. 3- aur Auzaai , Sufiyan Sory aur deegar logon ney ba-tareeq : (Yaahya bin Saeed an Urwaa an Aaysha) riwayat ki hai. 4- baaz ehle-ilm key nazdik amal isi hadees par hai, wo kehtey hain : jab aadmi aetikaf ka irada karey to Fajr padhey , phir apney moa'takif (aetikaf ki jagah) mein dakhil ho jaey, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Ibrahim bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai. baaz kehtey hain : jab aadmi aetikaf ka irada karey to agley din jis mein wo aetikaf karna chahta hai ki raat ka suraj doob jaey to wo apney moa'takif (aetikaf ki jagah) mein betha ho, ye Sufiyan Sory aur Malik bin Anas ka qol hai."
792,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Ramzan key aakhiri ashrey mein aetikaf kartey aur farmatey : ''Shabe-qadr ko Ramzan key aakhiri ashrey mein talash karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein umr , Abi , Jabir bin Samura , Jabir bin Abdullah , ibne-Umar , Faltaan bin Aasim , Anas , abu Saeed Khudri , Abdullah bin Unais , abu-Bakra , ibne-Abbas , Bilal aur Ubada bin Samit (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- « یُجَاوِرُ » key maana « یَعْتَکِفُ » ''aetikaf kartey they'' key hain. 4- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi (riwayat hui) aksar riwayaat yehi hain ke aap ney farmaya : ''isey aakhiri ashrey ki tamam taaq raaton mein talash karo.'' aur Shabe-qadr key silsiley mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ikkeeswin, teiswin, pachchiswin, sattaaisween, unteesween aur Ramzan ki aakhiri raat key aqwal (baaten) marvi (riwayat hui) hain, Shafai kehtey hain ke merey nazdik is ka mafhoom (واللہ اعلم) ye hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam har saail (sawal karne wale) ko uskey sawal key mutabiq jawab detey they. aap sey kaha jata : hum isey falan raat mein talash karen? aap farmatey : haan falan raat mein talash karo. 5- Shafai kehtey hain : merey nazdik sab sey qawi riwayat ikkeeswin raat ki hai. 6- Ubai-bin Kaab sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai wo qism kha kar kehtey ke ye sattaaiisween raat hai. kehtey ke hamein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney uski alamaten bataeen, hamney isey ginkar yad rakha. abu-Qulaba sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke Shae-qadr aakhiri ashrey mein muntaqil hoti rehti hai."
793,"Mainey Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : Abul Munzir ! aap ko kaisey malum huwa ke ye sattaaisween raat hai? to unhoney kaha : kyon nahin, hamein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney khabar di hai ke ''ye eik aisi raat hai jiski subah jab suraj nikleyga to is mein shuaa (kiran) nahin hogi, to humne ginti ki aur humne yad rakha. (Zarr kehtey hain) Allah ki qism ! ibne-Masood ko bhi malum hai ke wo Ramzan mein hai aur wo sattaaisween raat hai. lekin wo ye napasand kartey hain ke tumhen (isey musalmano ! ko) bata den aur tum takiya kar ke beth jaao. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
794,"Mujh sey merey baap ney bayan kiya ke abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) key paas Shabe-qadr ka zikr kiya gaya to unhoney kaha : ''jis chiz ki wajeh sey main isey sirf aakhiri ashrey hi mein talash karta hun wo ye hai ke mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey eik baat suni hai, mainey aap ko farmatey suna hai : ''talash karo jab (mahina pura honey mein) no din baqi reh jaeyn, ya jab saat din baqi reh jaeyn , ya jab paanch din reh jaeyn , ya jab teen din reh jaeyn.'' Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) Ramzan key bees din namaz padhtey they jaisey purey saal padhtey they lekin jab aakhiri ushra aata to ibadat mein khub mehnat kartey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
795,Ke Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Ramzan ke aakhiri ashrey mein apney ghar walon ko jagaatey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
796,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aakhiri ashrey mein ibadat mein itni koshish kartey they jitni doosrey dino mein nahin kartey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai.
797,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' thanda-thanda baghair mehnat ka maale-ghanimat ye hai ke roza sardi mein ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees mursal hai. Aamir bin Masood ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko nahin paya . ye Ibrahim bin Aamir Qarshi key walid hain jin sey Shoba aur Sauri ney riwayat ki hai.
798,jab aayate-karima : (وعلى الذين يطيقونه فدية طعام مسكين) ''aur un logon par jo rozey ki taqat rakhtey hain eik miskeen ko khana khilaney ka fidya hai'' (AlBqraa :184) utri to hum mein sey jo chahta ke roza na rakhey wo fidya dey deta yahan tak ke uskey baad wali padhi. aayat nazil hui aur usney isey mansookh kar diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai.
799,"Main Ramzan mein Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaya , wo safar ka irada kar rahey they, un ki sawari par kajaawa kasaa ja chuka tha aur wo safar key kapdey pehan chukey they, unhoney khana mangaayaa aur khaya. mainey un sey puchha : ye sunnat hai? kaha : haan sunnat hai. phir wo sawar huye."
800,"Muhammad bin Kaab sey riwayat hai ke main Ramzan mein Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaya phir unhoney isi tarah zikr kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- aur Muhammad bin Jaafar hi ibne-Abi Kasir Madeeni hain aur bharosemand hain aur yehi Ismail bin Jaafar key bhai hain aur Abdullah bin Jaafar Ali bin Abdullah Madeeni key walid ibne Najeeh hain, Yahya bin Moayan inko zaeef thehratey they. 3- baaz ehle-ilm isi hadees ki taraf gaey hain, wo kehtey hain ke musafir key liye jayez hai ke wo apney ghar sey nikalney sey pehley iftaar karey lekin usey namaz qasr karney ki ijazat nahin jab tak ke shehar ya gaaon ki faseel sey bahar na nikal jaey. yehi Is-haq bin Ibrahim bin Raahviya Hanzali ka qol hai."
801,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''roze-daar ka tohfa khushbudar tel aur ood ki angheeti hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- iski sanad qawi nahin hai. 3- hum isey sirf Saad bin Tareef ki riwayat sey jantey hain.  4- Saad bin Tareef zaeef qarar diye jatey hain.
802,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Eidul-Fitr ka din wo hai jab log Eid manaaein, aur Eidul-Azha ka din wo hai jis din log qurbani karen.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees , is sanad sey Hasan gharib sahih hai. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey puchha : kya Muhammad bin Munkadir ney Aaisha sey suna hai? unhoney kaha : haan , wo apni riwayat mein kehtey hain : mainey Aaisha sey suna."
803,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Ramzan key aakhiri ashrey mein aetikaf kartey they, eik saal aap aetikaf nahin kar sakey to jab aglaa saal aaya to aap ney bees din ka aetikaf kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas bin Malik ki ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- moa'takif (aetikaf kiye hue) jab apna aetikaf us muddat key pura karney sey pehley khatam kar dey jiski usney niyat ki thi to is barey mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai. baaz ehle-ilm ney kaha : jab wo aetikaf tod dey to is par qaza wajib hogi unhoney is hadees sey daleel pakdi hai jis mein hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apney aetikaf sey nikal aaye to aap ney shawwaal mein das din ka aetikaf kiya, ye Malik ka qol hai. aur baaz kehtey hain : agar is par aetikaf ki nazar ya koi aisi chiz na ho jisey usney apney ooper wajib kar li ho aur wo nafl ki niyat sey aetikaf mein raha ho phir aetikaf sey nikal aaya ho to is par qaza wajib nahin siwaye iske ke wo apni pasand sey usey chahey aur ye is par wajib nahin hoga. yehi Shafai ka qol hai. 3- Shafai kehtey hain : har wo amal jis key karney ya na karney key silsiley main tumhen ikhtiyar ho jab tum usey karna shuru kar do phir uskey pura honey sey pehley tum usey chhod do to uski qaza tum par lazim nahin hai. siwaye Haj aur Umra ke. 4- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
804,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab aetikaf mein hotey to apna sar merey qarib kar detey mein is mein kanghi kar deti padhi. aur aap ghar mein kisi insani zarurat key ilawa padhi. dakhil nahin hotey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isi tarah isey deegar kaee logon ney bhi ba-tareeq : (Maalik an ibne Shahab an Urwaa, umra an Aaysha) riwayat kiya hai, baaz logon ney isey ba-tareeq : (Maalik an ibne Shahab an Urwaa, umra an Aaysha) riwayat kiya hai, aur sahih ye hai ke ibne Shahab Zohri ney isey Urwa aur Umra dono sey aur un dono ney Aaisha sey riwayat kiya hai."
805,"Basanad (Ilyaas bin Saad an ibneShahaab an Umraah,Urwaa an Aaysha) riwayat kiya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- aur ehle-ilm key nazdik isi par amal hai ke jab aadmi aetikaf karey to insani zarurat key baghair apney moa'takif  (aetikaf ki jagah) sey na nikley, aur inka is baat par ittifaq hai ke wo pakhana peshab jaisi apni zarooraton ko pura karney key liye nikal sakta hai. 2- phir moa'takif (aetikaf kiye hue) key liye mareez ki iyaadat karney, Jume aur janaze mein shareek honey mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai, Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ki raey hai ke wo mareez ki iyaadat kar sakta hai, janaze key sath ja sakta hai aur Jume mein shareek ho sakta hai jabke usney iski shart laga li ho. ye Sufiyan Sory aur ibne-Mubarak ka qol hai. 3- aur baaz log kehtey hain ke usey in mein sey koi bhi chiz karney ki ijazat nahin, unka khayal hai ke moa'takif (aetikaf kiye hue) key liye zaruri hai ke jab wo kisi aisey shehar mein ho jahan Juma hota ho to Jaama Masjid main hi aetikaf karey. isliye ke ye log Jume key liye apney moa'takif (aetikaf ki jagah) sey nikalna uskey liye makrooh qarar detey hain aur uskey liye Juma chhodney ko bhi jayez nahin samajhtey, isliye unka kehna hai ke wo Jaama Masjid hi mein aetikaf karey taake usey insani hajiton key ilawa kisi aur hajat sey bahar nikalney ki zarurat na baqi rahey, isliye ke baghair kisi insani zarurat key masjid sey nikalney sey aetikaf toot jata hai, yehi Malik aur Shafai ka qol hai. 4- aur Ahmed kehtey hain : Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees ki taraf sey na wo mareez ki iyaadat karega, na janaze key sath jaeyga. 5- Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain : agar wo in chizon ki shart kar ley to usey janaazey key sath janey aur mareez ki iyaadat karney ki ijazat hai."
806,"hamney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath Ramzan ke rozey rakhey to aap ney hameni namaze (Tarawih) nahin padhaai, yahan tak ke Ramzan key sirf saat din baqi reh gaey to aap ney hamarey saath qiyaam kiya (yani tahajjud padhi) yahan tak ke eik tihai raat guzar gaee. phir jab chhe raaten reh gaeen to aap ney hamarey sath qiyam nahin kiya. (yani tahajjud nahin padhi) aur jab paanch raaten reh gaeen to aap ney hamarey sath qiyam kiya (yani tahajjud padhi) yahan tak ke aadhi raat ho gaee. to hamney aap sey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! agar aap is raat key baqi hissey mein bhi hamein nafl padhatey rehtey (to behtar hota)? aap ney farmaya : ''jisney Imam key sath qiyam kiya yahan tak ke wo farigh ho jaey to uskey liye puri raat ka qiyam likha jaeyga, phir aap ney hamein namaz nahin padhaai, yahan tak ke mahiney key sirf teen din baqi reh gaey, phir aap ney hamen sattaaisween raat ko namaz padhaai. aur apney ghar walon aur apni aurton ko bhi bulaya , aap ney hamarey sath qiyam kiya yahan tak ke hamen 'falah' key chhoot janey ka andesha huwa. (Raavi kehtey hain) mainey puchha : 'falah' kya chiz hai? to unhoney kaha : sehri hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha , Noman bin Bashir aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Ramzan key qiyam key silsiley mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai. baaz logon ka khayal hai ke witr key sath iktaalis rakatein padheyga, ye ehale-Madina ka qol hai, unkey nazdik Madiney mein isi par amal tha. 4- aur aksar ehle-ilm in hadeeson ki bina par jo umr , Ali aur doosrey Sahaba kiram (Raziallauh anhum) sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai bees rakat key qaail hain. ye Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak aur Shafai ka qol hai. aur Shafai kehtey hain : isi tarah sey mainey apney shehar Makkey mein paya hai ke bees rakatein padhtey they. 5- Ahmed kehtey hain : is silsiley mein kaee qism ki baaten marvi (riwayat hui) hain padhi. unhoney is silsiley mein koi faisla-kun baat nahin kahi. 6- Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain : hamen Ubai-bin Kaab ki riwayat key mutabiq 41 rakatein marghoob hain. 7- ibne-Mubarak , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ney maahe-Ramzan mein Imam key sath namaz padhney ko pasand kiya hai. 8- Shafai ney akeley padhney ko pasand kiya hai jab wo Qaari ho."
807,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney kisi roze-daar ko iftaar karaya to usey bhi uskey barabar sawab milega , baghair iskey ke roze-daar key sawab mein sey zara bhi kam kiya jaey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
808,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Ramzan key qiyam ( tahajjud padhney ( ki targheeb dilaatey , baghair iskey ke unhen taakidi hukm den aur farmatey : ''jisney eman key sath sawab ki niyat sey Ramzan mein qiyam kiya to uskey guzishta (pichhle) gunah bakhsh diye jaeyngey.''  chunanche Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wafat ho gaee aur maamla isi par qaaim raha, phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key ehad khilaafat mein aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) key ehad khilaafat key ibtidaai daur mein bhi maamla isi par raha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi sey hadees aai hai. 3- ye hadees b-tareeq : (Zohri an Urwaa an Aaysha an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat ki hai."
